items.name: hibiki
items.description: Hibiki is a model for streaming speech translation (also known as simultaneous translation). Unlike offline translation—where one waits for the end of the source utterance to start translating--- Hibiki adapts its flow to accumulate just enough context to produce a correct translation in real-time, chunk by chunk.
